                            <comment id="14545371" author="srowen" created="Fri, 15 May 2015 11:49:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A-ha. I think the issue is that additional args to &lt;tt&gt;start-master.sh&lt;/tt&gt; aren&apos;t passed through to &lt;tt&gt;Master&lt;/tt&gt; with &quot;$@&quot;. I think they are intended to be, as the same thing is done in &lt;tt&gt;start-slave.sh&lt;/tt&gt; for example. Let me look a little more and open a PR if it seems like the right thing to do.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
